(6, 'Introduction to JavaScript', 'JavaScript fundamentals', 'Understand the fundamentals of JavaScript,\nLearn how to manipulate the DOM,\nExplore JavaScript libraries and frameworks', 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'Java_script.jpg'),
(7, 'Python Programming: The Basics', 'Gain essential skills for writing Python', 'Master Python fundamentals and syntax, Use control structures and loops effectively, Perform file handling operations, Understand object-oriented programming (OOP) in Python', 0, 1, 2, NULL, 'Python_Thumbnail_b6e99c74df.png'),
(8, 'Lisp Unleashed', 'Exploring Functional Programming', 'Understand the fundamental concepts of Lisp programming, Explore the unique features and syntax of Lisp, Master functional programming principles and techniques, Learn how to write and evaluate Lisp expressions, Gain proficiency in working with Lisp data structures, Discover the power of recursion and higher-order functions in Lisp', 1, 1, 4, NULL, NULL),
(9, 'TypeScript Essentials\n\n', 'Building Scalable and Type-Safe Applications', 'Understand the fundamentals of TypeScript and its role in building JavaScript applications, Learn how to set up a TypeScript development environment and integrate it into your workflow,Gain knowledge of TypeScript\'s type system and its benefits for catching errors and improving code quality', 0, 1, 3, NULL, NULL),
(14, 'Java Jumpstart: From Novice to Java Pro', 'Fast-track your Java skills from beginner to pro with Java Jumpstart', 'Understand the fundamental concepts of Java programming, Learn about variables and control structures in Java, Gain knowledge of object-oriented programming principles and apply them in Java, Explore classes and objects in Java, Understand how to handle exceptions and errors in Java programs, Learn about input/output operations and file handling in Java', 0, 1, 2, NULL, NULL),
(16, 'Julia Mastery and Scientific Computing', 'Mastering Scientific Computing and Data Analysis', 'Gain a solid understanding of the Julia programming language and its unique features,Learn to write efficient and performant code for scientific computing tasks, Explore Julia\'s powerful ecosystem of packages and libraries for various domains, Understand how to leverage Julia\'s advanced features, such as multiple dispatch and metaprogramming, Develop proficiency in solving complex mathematical and scientific problems using Julia, Acquire knowledge of best practices and techniques for optimizing Julia code.\nFamiliarize yourself with parallel and distributed computing in Julia for scaling computations', 1, 1, 3, 79.99, 'fitness_bootcamp.jpg'),
(18, 'C# Masterclass: From Beginner to Pro', 'C# Essentials: A Comprehensive Guide to Modern Development', 'Understand the fundamentals of C# programming language, Explore object-oriented programming (OOP) concepts in C# and learn to design and implement classes and objects, Gain proficiency in using C# language features such as properties and methodsto encapsulate functionality and promote code reuse, Master the concepts of exception handling and error management to create robust and reliable C# applications, Learn to work with collections and utilize C#\'s built-in data structures to store and manipulate data efficiently, Understand and implement advanced C# features such as generics and lambda expressions to write more flexible and reusable code', 0, 1, 2, NULL, 'c_sharp.png'),
(19, 'Rust: Crafting Robust and Rusty Systems', 'How to see sounds', 'Master Rust\'s concurrency model using threads and async/await, Develop high-performance Rust applications with efficient code execution, Build robust and safe systems using Rust\'s ownership model and error handling, Work with the Rust ecosystem including libraries and tooling, Apply Rust to real-world projects with best practices and design patterns', 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'soundscapes.png'),
(33, 'Digital Marketing', 'A comprehensive course on Digital Marketing', 'Understand the fundamental concepts and principles of digital marketing, Identify and analyze different digital marketing channels and their advantages and limitations, Develop a comprehensive digital marketing strategy aligned with business goals and target audience, Optimize websites for improved user experience and better conversion rates, Implement effective search engine optimization (SEO) techniques to improve organic visibility and website traffic, Create and manage successful pay-per-click (PPC) advertising campaigns on platforms like Google Ads, Utilize social media platforms to effectively engage with the target audience and promote brand awareness, \nDevelop and execute targeted email marketing campaigns to nurture leads and drive conversions', 1, 1, 2, NULL, 'Unknown.jpeg'),
(56, 'Ruby for Professionals', 'Description', 'Objectives', 0, 1, 2, NULL, NULL);
